(44, 9, 8, 44, 9, 18, 18, 'saw no man', 'Saul''s Transformation and Baptism', 'This connection highlights Saul''s physical blindness and subsequent healing. Both passages emphasize his journey from darkness to sight, culminating in his baptism.', 'theme', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
