(44, 9, 13, 26, 3, 14, 14, NULL, 'Connection of Spiritual Struggle', 'This connection highlights the emotional turmoil experienced by both Ananias and Ezekiel. Ananias expresses bitterness and fear regarding Saul''s actions, while Ezekiel describes going in bitterness and heat of spirit, indicating a shared theme of struggle in responding to divine calling.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
